# Movie Ratings and Popularity Analysis

## Project Overview
This project explores movie ratings, popularity, genres, and audience trends using data analysis techniques in Python.

## Tools Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn

## Key Insights
- Popular movies tend to receive more audience votes
- Certain genres consistently achieve higher ratings
- Data analysis helps identify entertainment trends and viewer preferences

## Dataset
TMDB Movies Dataset
